Class PlanitNetworkWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.goplanit.converter.BaseWriterImpl<T>

        • org.goplanit.io.converter.network.PlanitNetworkWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConverterEntity, ConverterWriter<LayeredNetwork<?,​?>>, NetworkWriter
    public class PlanitNetworkWriter
extends PlanitWriterImpl<LayeredNetwork<?,​?>>
implements NetworkWriter
    Writer to persist a PLANit network to disk in the native PLANit format. By default the xml ids are used for writing out the ids in the XML.
    Author:
    markr
